: 1600 lbs Time Since Last Inspection: 30 Hours Engines: 1 Reciprocating Airframe Total Time: 8036 Hours Engine Manufacturer: Continental ELT: Installed, not activated Engine Model/Series: O-200 Registered Owner: TEVIS AVIATION, INC.
